ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Assetbundle
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
local inner

function onSave()
    if inner ~= nil then
        return JSON.encode({innerGUID = inner.guid})
    end
end

function onLoad(scriptState)
    --Remove abandoned inner mobility object
    if scriptState ~= nil then
        local toDelete = JSON.decode(scriptState)
        if toDelete ~= nil and toDelete.innerGUID ~= nil then
            local oldInner = getObjectFromGUID(toDelete.innerGUID)
            if oldInner ~= nil then
                oldInner.destruct()
            end
        end
    end
    --Spawn inner mobility object; wait to avoid issues with certain containers
    Wait.time(spawnInner, 1)
end

function spawnInner()
    inner = spawnObject({
            type = "Custom_Assetbundle",
            position = self.getPosition(),
            sound = false,
            callback_function = setInner
    })
    inner.setCustomObject({assetbundle = "https://steamusercontent-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/1870681849506449071/9433157C60FF86C1AA598350DB85053510637354/"})
    Wait.time(check, 1, -1)
    Wait.time(play, math.random(10, 120), -1)
end

function setInner()
    inner.drag_selectable = false
    inner.use_gravity = false
    inner.tooltip = false
end

function check()
    local height = self.getPosition().y
    if height < -15 then
        self.setPosition({0, 30, 0})
    elseif height < 5 then
        self.addForce(vector(0, 20, 0), 4)
    end
end

function play()
    self.AssetBundle.playTriggerEffect(0)
end

function onUpdate()
    if inner ~= nil then
        inner.setPosition(self.getPosition())
    end
end

function onDestroy()
    destroyInner()
end

function destroyInner()
    if inner ~= nil then
        destroyObject(inner)
        inner = nil
    end
end

function onObjectEnterContainer(container, object)
    if object == self then
        destroyInner()
    end
end
